This is a frontend-only change: add the fields to the ToolGrammarModifiers interface and the OptionsBar UI. PlanCanvas wiring is a follow-up workpackage.

## Files to modify

1. `packages/web/src/tools/toolGrammar.ts` — add two fields to ToolGrammarModifiers
